data.description: Welcome to your dream two-family residence tucked away on a private street in Staten Island. This extraordinary property presents a lavish and spacious living experience, boasting 6 bedrooms, 6 bathrooms, 2 car garage, a fully finished basement, and an impressive 4,800 square feet of opulent living space.  Upon arrival, you'll be captivated by the stunning curb appeal of this prestigious home. The exterior showcases elegant architectural design, meticulous landscaping, and a grand entrance that sets the tone for the unparalleled luxury within. The sprawling floor plan provides an abundance of space for both entertaining and relaxation. From the moment you enter the gracious foyer, you'll be greeted by exquisite details, including soaring ceilings, designer lighting fixtures, and premium finishes throughout.The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, custom cabinetry, a center island, and a generous pantry. It seamlessly flows into the spacious dining area, perfect for hosting elegant dinner parties or casual family gatherings.The luxurious master suite is a true sanctuary, offering a serene retreat from the outside world. With its private sitting area, and a spa-like en-suite bathroom, complete with a soaking tub, dual vanities, and a walk-in shower, this master suite exudes sophistication and tranquility. Each bedroom is generously sized, ensuring that family members or guests enjoy the ultimate comfort and privacy. The bathrooms throughout the home are appointed with high-end fixtures and finishes, embodying a sense of luxury and style. In addition, this home offers a large, fully renovated 1 bedroom second-floor apartment.Step outside into your own private oasis, where you'll find an impressive backyard retreat. The meticulously landscaped grounds offer an inviting atmosphere for outdoor entertaining, with a spacious patio, a built-in barbecue area, and a large inground pool, creating an idyllic setting
